Package: HEART
Type: Package
Title: A high-efficiency and robust test for large scale single-cell RNA-sequencing differential expression analysis
Version: 1.1.0
Author: Xin Yuan
Maintainer: Xin Yuan <yuanxin_yx@sjtu.edu.cn>
Description: HEART, a statistical combination test, 
	can easily capture the various source of the difference beyond mean 
	expression changesand facilitate the accuracy, robustness, 
	and efficiency of single-cell DE analysis.
